Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:30.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小日向
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.15,0:04:33.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她身着的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道和那个时候一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刻印　启动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来　一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么　翼小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.41,0:04:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切皆乃为国尽忠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.58,0:05:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟用大范围攻击压制
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无差别攻击也太反常…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.73,0:05:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动作被封住了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:19.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾乃国之防人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.71,0:05:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一连串事件的幕后黑手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然是风鸣机关
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此我也相信她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.16,0:05:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人那么笨拙怎么可能做出背叛这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.56,0:05:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没有怀疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼小姐是我们重要的同伴Death
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是被那双魔眼给…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:05:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单独叫我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.06,0:05:55.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs32}速至司令部
