Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此乃与吾国相称之神之力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.78,0:06:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藉由直通回馈系统之脑控行将完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.78,0:06:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(542.666,670.333)}Direct Feedback System
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,届时便是新时代之威慑力诞生之日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:26.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但樱井女士已然故去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:28.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是如何造出新Symphogear
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此非Symphogear
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃神兽镜之Faust-Robe是也
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.82,0:06:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然铸就此物者已不知葬身何处矣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心中回响着非如此不可的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时便毫不犹豫地行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:54.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转念想来　那真的是正确的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.29,0:06:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.38,0:07:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何故未将其斩尽杀绝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.97,0:07:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那　那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.85,0:07:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也罢　但切莫迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那般弱小之内心终难担大任
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.65,0:07:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为守家护国化作恶鬼便是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌声断无从拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.18,0:07:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事找我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.89,0:07:26.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉　突然叫你过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间紧迫　有新的任务要交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.09,0:07:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经由多日的秘密调查以及政治手段
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:38.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对风鸣宗家强行搜查的准备完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.78,0:07:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就要出发
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风鸣宗家是你们和翼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的　已经刻不容缓了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因违反风鸣讣堂亲自推行的护国灾害派遣法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受日本政府所托加以逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:08:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据情况　当场击毙也已被批准
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,击毙　对翼也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:09.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故而做出了此事不能交给因违规正在禁闭的响
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及其他未成年成员的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以只叫了玛利亚小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽是任务　但恕我不能苟同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.38,0:08:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍者就是将心置于刀刃之下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何　血亲相残都是不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是为了将翼绑回来才和你们一起去的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.11,0:08:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然中途就意识到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.44,0:08:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但怎么想都是我根本帮不上忙的事儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是你说要我说给你听的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.27,0:08:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话是这么说啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我或许是被诅咒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开门
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,0:09:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我权限内的安防措施都可以解除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.72,0:09:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽速拘捕风鸣讣堂及相关人员
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.56,0:09:34.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Alca-NOISE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.02,0:09:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:41.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛利亚　Amalgam暂时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想吃禁闭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:45.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有劳了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若再违反协定 S.O.N.G.今后或将无法在日本行动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.14,0:09:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于预定时间开始交战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但行动限制尚未完全解除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:10:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.49,0:10:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧搜查　扣押相关证据
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.65,0:10:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请随我来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摇尾乞怜于联合国之逆子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何事竟敢恬面至此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自是为劝阻您
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.30,0:10:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊　这才对嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好见到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.81,0:10:58.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有太多事等你解释了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:10:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.45,0:11:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对风鸣讣堂唯命是从就是你所谓的防人之道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.45,0:11:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(855,670.333)}守
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.45,0:11:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(895,670.333)}护
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.45,0:11:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(935,670.333)}众
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.45,0:11:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(975,670.333)}生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然也
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神之力亦乃为此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.12,0:11:21.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何等冷血的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此间安容尔多言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快想一想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的容身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.93,0:11:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的亲密战友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.63,0:11:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有你生而为你的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我生为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.28,0:11:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是什么神之力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:43.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以你一己之力守护众生的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毋需赘言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,众生无力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此　更需绝世之力加以守护
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.18,0:12:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无力就需要守护　这是何等傲慢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所言何意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这话简直像说不守护什么人就无法自立一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.79,0:12:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么时候开始从守护他人变成独善其身的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.70,0:12:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,护庇羸弱不成其为理由…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.97,0:12:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我又是为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.58,0:12:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整天如痴如狂地防人防人不离口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白　我不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,败吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.96,0:14:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尔若一心取吾性命…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.24,0:14:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无能若斯　枉为吾子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.51,0:14:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在外面打得正热闹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我们的机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把神之力的管理权限改为我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风鸣讣堂如此轻易抛弃我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不报复我咽不下这口气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好　先将直通回馈系统…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(701.333,672.999)}Direct Feedback System
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.37,0:14:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.55,0:14:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂　这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾露莎　米蕾娅克
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.81,0:14:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吧　翼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到大家的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.73,0:15:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.80,0:15:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吾身边　翼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.51,0:15:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若为防人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.35,0:15:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若仍流有风鸣之血
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:12.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经连应倚仗什么都不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刻印　启动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.37,0:15:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尔亦欲令风鸣蒙羞乎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不肖逆子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.98,0:15:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟又有犬子现身乎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:15:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲您为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.47,0:16:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想让别的男人以你的父亲自居啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.68,0:16:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们并非因众生无力而加以守护
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.42,0:16:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是因为他们有值得守护的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要牢记于心…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命已呜呼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忤逆犯上　业有应得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,值得守护的价值究竟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:45.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚不成熟的我暂且无从得知
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:47.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.86,0:16:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还请您倾听我的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.68,0:17:00.69,IN_T_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}Imyuteus amenohabakiri tron
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\pos(1262,21)}风轮火斩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.59,0:18:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(944,64)}却有何用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.17,0:18:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以肉身凌驾于Gear之上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.01,0:18:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌声无从守护世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.26,0:18:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相通相解不过痴人说梦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.24,0:18:33.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尔颂此等狂言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.21,0:18:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何颜以对抛颅洒血为国捐躯之先烈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.64,0:18:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却仍执迷不悟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶　赶上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.78,0:19:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾生之刃群蜘蛛竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国之所需并非防人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.04,0:19:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃是护国恶鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾舍命化护国恶鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尔亦终堕…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.61,0:19:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,护国恶鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了　翼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.48,0:20:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若你也堕为恶鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.68,0:20:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就无颜面对老哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地震？这震动是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.04,0:20:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不　你看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:33.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好　好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我的禁闭…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:39.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了　马上赶回总部
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.89,0:20:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.46,0:20:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.28,0:20:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说响啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事　小问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.24,0:20:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是没法为你做什么的废材老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.72,0:20:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一能说给女儿听的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:04.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样一句话对没有骨气的我不知何时变成了诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你不一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.34,0:21:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:17.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把一件事当成诅咒或是祝福全在一念之间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.02,0:21:21.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诅咒…说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且　你看　那什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:28.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「咒」和「祝」的读音其实很像的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.49,0:21:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以互为正反…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.19,0:21:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我说的话也不都是错的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.49,0:21:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明年的这时候肯定会变成名言的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确会变成名言呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.14,0:21:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油吧　响
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.92,0:21:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.18,0:21:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢啦　爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.49,0:21:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉面很好吃
